  <p class="text-center">
    Plugin je open-source a dostupný na <strong>Figma Community</strong>.
  </p>
  <br />
  <p class="text-center">
    <strong>CSS Variables Converter & Exporter</strong>
  </p>
  <br />
  <p class="text-center" style="font-size: 0.8em; opacity: 0.7;">
    figma.com/community/plugin/1580865604483451262
  </p>
  <br />
  <p class="text-center" style="font-size: 0.8em; opacity: 0.7;">
    github.com/Luko248/figma-variables-converter-and-exporter
  </p>
</Slide>
